<br>
I have been following this board quite a bit, but haven't posted much.  I figured it was time I share a few ideas.<br>
<br>
Skalds have been wanting some skills which make them more useful to groups, so here are a few ideas for our BS line.  (I always find it funny our line is called BS)<br>
<br>
*Group End shout on a 5 minute timer - This shout inspires our Viking brethren to have a second wind.  This won't replace shammy buff, but adds a nice touch to skalds to make them more usable by groups.  As level increases, end gain grows up to 100% end boost at 50th level BS skill.  This would give incentive to skalds to spec lvl 50 in songs.<br>
<br>
*PBAOE debuff shout. - There are plenty of pbaoe damage spells out there, so a debuff would be a little different.  Mid classes are a bit lacking in debuffs vs the other realms.  This fits with a skald also...our shouts weaken or strike fear into enemies that are near.<br>
<br>
*Celerity shout or chant - Only makes sense that a skald would have this.  Skalds songs in battle were meant to boost the prowess of the viking brethren in combat.<br>
<br>
I'd trade all the resist chants for a few useful chants or shouts like this.  All these are group friendly, and not overpowered or unbalancing.  What do you all think? <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showPrevMessage?topicID=677.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showNextMessage?topicID=677.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=677.topic&index=5><img src=http://www.stuckathome.com/skalded/images/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=677.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.threadControl?topicID=677.topic><img src=http://www.stuckathome.com/skalded/images/closethread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=677.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=677.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub36.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table bo